    // In-game Desc:
    // "Starts out with +30% damage. Rip and Tear!" - ihaz
      +30% Damage Bonus
      +50% faster firing speed

      -66% clip size
      +20% slower reload time
      -40% max ammo
      No random crits
      (HIDDEN) Turns victim to dismembered gibs.
      (HIDDEN, COMMENTED OUT) -90% less accurate

      This weapon reloads its entire clip at once

