//===============
Secondary
    1. Pistol
	 • Balanced Overclock: Critical Combo // On Kill: 5 seconds of critical hits +25% damage +100% ammo capacity -Is honorbound
-- Broken. No doubt. Broken. Secondaries should only cap at free minicrits.
    -- 
      On Kill: 5s of Critboost
      +25% damage bonus
      +100% max ammo

      Honourbound: Once drawn, pistolwhip yourself for 50 damage to yourself, unless it kills

    3. Winger
	 • Balanced Overclock: Royal Flight // Alt-Fire to dash forward every 3 seconds +400 stomp damage -25% jump height while active
-- Cool gimmick. Unfortunately 400 dmg every 3 sec, is nothing in MvM. Scout has a gun.
    --
      +15% damage bonus
      +25% greater jump height when active
      Deals 3x falling damage to the player you land on
      +100% increased falling damage force

      -60% clip size

    4. Bonk! Atomic Punch
	 • Balanced Overclock: Temporary Quick-Fix Uber // Replaces bonk effect with temporary Quick-Fix Uber
-- 
    --
      Drink to heal to full for 8 seconds. 

    6. Flying Guillotine
	 • Balanced Overclock: 4000 Degrees Knife // Always deals critical damage -30% primary ammo capacity
-- Weak, but niche Combo finisher vs vacc meds in this mission.
    --
      100% critical hits from anywhere
      Throw at your enemies to make them bleed! Long distance hits reduce recharge time

      No random critical hits

    7. Mad Milk
	 • Unstable Overclock: Spicy Milk // Replaces milk effect with a high damage fireball
-- Unironically strong sidegrade that OTK a decent chunk of bullet-res squishies in this mission.
    --
      (HIDDEN) Attacks will launch 30 DMG fireball

      -70% damage penalty vs players
      -50% damage penalty vs giants

//===============
Melee
    1. Bat
	 • Perk: Overkill // +30% base health on kill +500% damage -200% swing speed
-- 175~ base DMG, 600~ crit. Has its niche on certain comp, but shame - it doesn't solve bison and DF bots.
    -- 
      +500% damage bonus
      On Kill: Gain +30 health on attack
      +80% crit damage resistance while deployed

      -75% crit damage multiplier
      -100% slower firing speed
      Random Crits	

    4. Candy Cane
	 • Clean Overclock: Shine // Attacks reflects projectiles +Blast vulnerability is activated while active +30% blast radius -60% swing speed
-- Neat gimmick. Shame there aren't really that many reflectable projectiles in this mission when it gets good.
    -- 
      On Kill: A small health pack is dropped
      +30% reflected rocket explosion radius

      +50% explosive damage vulnerability when deployed
      -40% slower firing speed

    6. Sandman
	 • Clean Overclock: Sportsman Pride // On Hit: Gain Concheror Effect for 4 seconds +15 max health -40% slower swing speed
-- Clean Sidegrade to Gunbai. No issue with this tbh.
    -- 
    Alt-Fire: Launches a ball that slows opponents
    On Hit: 4s Concheror boost

    -40% slower firing speed

    7. Sun-on-Stick // +50% base health on kill +500% damage +Speedboost on kill -200% swing speed -Extinguishes targets
	 • Perk: Sun God
-- Gimmick. Axtinguisher.
    -- 
      100% critical hit vs burning players
      +25% fire damage resistance while deployed
      +475% damage bonus
      On Kill: Gain +30 health on attack
      On Kill: 4s Speedboost
      Mini-crits burning targets and extinguishes them

      -100% slower firing speed
      Random Crits	

    8. Wrap Assassin
	 • Balanced Overclock: Milky Balls // Applies milk for 2 seconds -30% health from packs
-- Sidegrade to Milk Pretty much. Except, it's just kind of mediocre. Straight upgrade.
    -- 
    +25% increase in recharge rate
    Alt-Fire: Launches a festive ornament that shatters causing bleed
    On Hit: target is  Mad Milked for 5s

    -65% damage penalty
    -30 max health on wearer

